<div class="title">More Pleasant This Way</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=NickAtNight&Exact=1">NickAtNight</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; NickAtNight. "More Pleasant This Way: An Experience with Amanita muscaria (exp44915)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Oct 3, 2008. erowid.org/exp/44915</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
<tr><td></td><td width="15">&nbsp;</td></tr>
</table>

